reviewText: I am disappointed in this DVD.  Most of the shown on the cover or shown on  the cover were nowhere to be seen on the DVD (unless there is a feature I'm  missing).  Some of the video was a bit dark as well.  Not sure it was worth  $9.99.
Have you ever walked down the street and wondered what that beautiful security guard would look like wrapped around you waist? Finally real women doing real things to the average Joe!
